# Agent node quick start

Edit EXPORTS first and set:

  CLOUDERA_REPO_USER
  CLOUDERA_REPO_PASS
  MANAGER_HOST

Then run:

  source ./EXPORTS
  ./RUN_AGENT

RUN_AGENT installs both Java 17 and Java 21 on agent nodes, installs the Cloudera Manager agent package, points it to MANAGER_HOST, and validates the node.
